ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of YVONNE PETERS of Winnipeg, Manitoba, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum for Human Rights, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Robyn Sneath, whose term has expired.
